claim.claim-text:
1. A combination sandwich press and grill device having a lower housing with a lower cooking surface and an upper housing with an upper cooking surface wherein:
the lower housing having a variable thermostat for controlling a lower cooking surface temperature;
the upper housing having a fixed thermostat for controlling an upper cooking surface temperature;
the lower housing being interconnected to the upper housing by a hinge;
the upper housing having a closed orientation, a fully open orientation and a locked intermediate orientation;
the lower housing receives a removable full length drip tray that collects drippings from both the lower cooking surface and the upper cooking surface when the device is in the fully open orientation; and
the drip tray is removable from the lower housing by sliding it out a front of the lower housing.
